        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Online Credit Card Disclosure Act of 2015</b></p> <p>Amends the Truth in Lending Act to require the billing statement of a consumer's account under an open end online credit plan to make specified disclosures in a conspicuous and prominent location on its webpage with each billing cycle.</p>]]></text>
